Text: RE ISDA Statement Cc feels like two yearsthank YOU kimberly for captaining the process Original Message From Kimberly Summe mailto Sent Friday September PM To Mark Taylor Mark Haedicke Bob Mancini Diane Genova Cc Robert Pickel Stacy Carey Ruth Ainslie Subject ISDA Statement Thank you for your input into the ISDA statement prepared over the past two years The statement has now been finalized and has been sent to various wire services including Reuters and Dow Jones and will be posted on our website wwwisdaorg under Whats New Kimberly Summe General Counsel
